    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n3774" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἔρις</span></b> , acc. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἔριδα</span> and <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἔριν</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">strife, contention, rivalry</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 1.8</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Il.
            7.210</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">; ἔριδα προφέρουσαι</span>, ‘putting forth
          rivalry,’ ‘vying with one another’ in speed, <i><span class="en">Od. 6.92</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">; ἔριδά τινι προφέρεσθαι ἀέθλων</span>,
          ‘challenge one to a contest for prizes,’ <i><span class="en">Od.
            8.210</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">; ἐξ ἔριδος</span>, ‘in rivalry,’ <i><span class="en">Il. 8.111</span></i>, <i><span class="en">Od.
            4.343</span></i>.—Personified, <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">Ἔρις</span>,
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">Discord</span>, <i><span class="en">Il. 11.73</span></i>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">. Ἔρῑς</span>, <i><span class="en">Il.
            4.440</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
